ws/184/player-profile/2010/05/01/1962446/world-cup-profile-iker-casillas-spain | title=Iker Casillas - Goalkeeper - Real Madrid - 20/05/1981 | website=www.goal.com | date=17 November 2011 | accessdate=15 June 2019}}<br>{{cite web | url=https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2914/champions-league/2014/05/22/4833425/iker-casillas-chasing-his-very-own-decima| title=Iker Casillas chasing his very own Decima | website=www.goal.com | date=22 May 2014 | accessdate=15 June 2019}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA European Under-16 Championship|UEFA European U-16 Championship]]: [[1997 UEFA European Under-16 Championship|1997]]<ref name=\"bleacher report\"/><ref name=\"goal\"/>\n*[[UEFA-CAF Meridian Cup]]: [[1999 UEFA-CAF Meridian Cup|1999]]<ref name=\"bleacher report\"/><ref name=\"goal\"/>\n\n===Individual===\nSource:<ref name=ikercasillasworld.com/>\n*[[Bravo Award]]: 2000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/bravo-awards.html|title=The \"Bravo\" Award|website=www.rsssf.com|accessdate=12 July 2014}}</ref>\n*[[Don Bal\u00f3n Award|La Liga Breakthrough Player of the Year]]: 2000\n*[[Ricardo Zamora Trophy|La Liga Zamora Trophy]]: [[2007\u201308 La Liga|2007\u201308]]\n*[[LFP Awards|La Liga Best Goalkeeper]]: [[LFP Awards|2009]], [[LFP Awards|2012]]\n*[[LFP Awards|La Liga Fair Play Award]]: [[LFP Awards|2012\u201313]]\n*[[Primeira Liga]] [[LPFP Awards|Fair Play Award]]: [[2017\u201318 Primeira Liga|2017\u201318]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/noticias/interior/bruno-fernandes-casillas-sergio-conceicao-todos-os-premios-da-liga-9562039.html|title=Bruno Fernandes, Casillas, S\u00e9rgio Concei\u00e7\u00e3o... Confira todos os premiados da Liga|trans-title=Bruno Fernandes, Casillas, S\u00e9rgio Concei\u00e7\u00e3o ... Check out all the winners of the League|website=www.ojogo.pt|language=pt|date=6 July 2018|accessdate=27 September 2018}}</ref>\n*MARCA Fair Play Award \u2013 MARCA's 80th Anniversary: 2018<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.zerozero.pt/news.php?id=237162|title=Casillas distinguido pela Marca com o pr\u00e9mio \u00abJogo Limpo\u00bb|website=www.zerozero.pt|language=pt|date=13 December 2018|accessdate=14 December 2018}}</ref>\n*Drag\u00f5es de Ouro Award \u2013 Porto Athlete of the Year: 2018<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/fc-porto/liga/dragoes-de-ouro-iker-casillas-foi-o-atleta-do-ano|title=Drag\u00f5es de Ouro: Iker Casillas foi o \u00abAtleta do Ano\u00bb|website=www.maisfutebol.iol.pt|language=pt|date=29 September 2018|accessdate=29 September 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Primeira Liga]] [[LPFP Awards|Best Goalkeeper]]: [[2018\u201319 Primeira Liga|2018\u201319]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ligaportugal.pt/pt/epocas/20192020/noticias/geral/kick-off-2019-20/vencedores-dos-premios-oficiais-da-liga-portugal-2018-2019/l|title=Vencedores dos Pr\u00e9mios Oficiais da Liga Portugal 2018-2019|website=www.ligaportugal.pt|language=pt|date=5 July 2019|accessdate=27 July 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Primeira Liga]] [[LPFP Awards|Team of the Year]]: [[2018\u201319 Primeira Liga|2018\u201319]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ligaportugal.pt/pt/epocas/20192020/noticias/geral/kick-off-2019-20/vencedores-dos-premios-oficiais-da-liga-portugal-2018-2019/l|title=Vencedores dos Pr\u00e9mios Oficiais da Liga Portugal 2018-2019|website=www.ligaportugal.pt|language=pt|date=5 July 2019|accessdate=27 July 2019}}</ref>\n*Quinas de Ouro Award \u2013 [[Primeira Liga]] Best XI: [[2018\u201319 Primeira Liga|2018\u201319]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/1a-liga/noticias/interior/quinas-de-ouro-melhor-onze-da-i-liga-com-casillas-e-dominado-por-benfica-e-fc-porto-11261512.htmlo|title=Quinas de Ouro: melhor onze da I Liga com Casillas e dominado por Benfica e FC Porto|website=www.ojogo.pt|language=pt|date=2 September 2019|accessdate=3 September 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Best European Goalkeeper]]: 2010\n*[[IFFHS World's Best Goalkeeper]]: 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012<ref name=\"Former Results\">{{cite web|url=http://iffhs.de/former-results/|title=Forme