st Costume Design\n| Mary E. Vogt\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Ensemble\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''Crazy Rich Asians''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Golden Globe Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[76th Golden Globe Awards|January 6, 2019]]\n| [[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy]]\n| {{Nominated}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/golden-globe-nominations-2019-1203082075/|title=Golden Globe Nominations: Complete List|last=Staff |first=Variety |date=December 6, 2018 |work=Variety |accessdate=December 6, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Golden Globe Award for Best Actress \u2013 Motion Picture Comedy or Musical|Best Actress in a Motion Picture \u2013 Comedy or Musical]]\n| Constance Wu\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Hollywood Film Awards]]\n| [[22nd Hollywood Film Awards|November 4, 2018]]\n| Breakout Ensemble Award\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''Crazy Rich Asians''\n| {{won|Honoree}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"HFA18\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/incredibles-2-hollywood-film-awards-honorees-1156216 |title=Hollywood Film Awards: 'Black Panther,' 'Incredibles 2' Among Latest Honorees |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=October 30, 2018|website=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=October 30, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Humanitas Prize]]\n| February 8, 2019\n| Comedy Feature Film\n| {{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref name=\"HP19\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/11/humanitas-prize-nominations-2018-list-black-panther-this-is-us-1202509603/ | title=Humanitas Prize: 'Black Panther', 'This Is Us' Among Nominations |last=Hipes |first=Patrick |date=November 27, 2018|website=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=November 27, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[International Cinematographers Guild|International Cinematographers Guild Publicists Awards]]\n| February 22, 2019\n